  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ジェニーの失われた言葉。英語学習要素を含むアドベンチャーゲーム。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Jenny’s on her way to the theater to practice for an upcoming role. Her script gets stolen though and has to track the pages down in different stages which are entered through the hub world. Once you collect a key and memorize letters and numbers, you go to the theater and use them to unlock the combination lock. Jenny has 2 abilities: punching and kicking, and after picking up powerups, throwing stars and bug spray",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Jenny is on her way to a rehearsal for an upcoming role in a musical, but her script gets stolen by the BB cult. She now has to retrieve it while avoiding the hitmen sent by the evil organization to kill her.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
